org.apache.cayenne.access.jdbc

Interface BatchQueryBuilderFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultBatchQueryBuilderFactory, SoftDeleteQueryBuilderFactory

    public interface BatchQueryBuilderFactory
    Factory which creates BatchQueryBuilders for different types of queries, which, in their turn, create SQL strings for batch queries.
    Since:
    3.0
